skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kicks one oh two point five
des:
The 4 States #1 for Country! Home of Randy & Jen in the morning!
Once enabled, just say: "Alexa, open kicks one oh two point five" and Alexa will guide you from there!
After that, you can say things like:
 * "Listen to on demand"
 * "Resume"
 * "On demand options"
When playing audio, you can say:
 * Alexa, pause
When playing on-demand content, you can skip to an older show by saying:
 * Alexa, next
And navigate to the previous segment by saying:
 * Alexa, go back
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
